#: src/29_writing_a_song.md:1
msgid "Chapter 29. Writing and Modifying a Song"
msgstr "第29章. 楽曲を書いて書き換える"

#: src/29_writing_a_song.md:5
msgid ""
"By the end of this chapter you will have changed a song and heard the "
