msgstr "`yield main(tick: Word) -> Word`"

#: src/AUTOMATION_SCRIPTING.md:44
msgid "Returns rather than yields"
msgstr "yield ではなく return します"

#: src/AUTOMATION_SCRIPTING.md:44
msgid "Cooperative task that pauses and resumes across ticks, then finishes."
msgstr "ティックをまたいで一時停止と再開を行い、その後終了する協調的タスク。"

#: src/AUTOMATION_SCRIPTING.md:45
msgid "Daemon"
msgstr "デーモン"

#: src/AUTOMATION_SCRIPTING.md:45
